/tr></table></figure></p><hr><h1 id="ABOUT-卡片中加入运行时间"><a href="#ABOUT-卡片中加入运行时间" class="headerlink" title="ABOUT 卡片中加入运行时间"></a>ABOUT 卡片中加入运行时间</h1><ul><li>在 footer.php 中添加如下代码<br>在<code>&lt;/p&gt;</code>前，添加<figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;span id=<span class="string">"djclock"</span>&gt;&lt;/span&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><p>在<code>&lt;/p&gt;</code>后，添加<br><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;script language=<span class="string">"javascript"</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">BirthDay1=<span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="built_in">Date</span>(<span class="string">"&lt;?php $this-&gt;options-&gt;otime(); ?&gt;"</span>);<span class="comment">//从站点配置中读取</span></span><br><span class="line">today1=<span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="built_in">Date</span>();</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title">THINPIGServerTime1</span>(<span class="params"></span>)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">today1.setTime(today1.getTime()+<span class="number">250</span>);</span><br><span class="line">timeold1=(today1.getTime()-BirthDay1.getTime());</span><br><span class="line">sectimeold1=timeold1/<span class="number">1000</span></span><br><span class="line">secondsold1=<span class="built_in">Math</span>.floor(sectimeold1);</span><br><span class="line">msPerDay1=<span class="number">24</span>*<span class="number">60</span>*<span class="number">60</span>*<span class="number">1000</span></span><br><span class="line">e_daysold1=timeold1/msPerDay1</span><br><span class="line">daysold1=<span class="built_in">Math</span>.floor(e_daysold1);</span><br><span class="line">e_hrsold1=(e_daysold1-daysold1)*<span class="number">24</span>;</span><br><span class="line">hrsold1=<span class="built_in">Math</span>.floor(e_hrsold1);</span><br><span class="line">e_minsold1=(e_hrsold1-hrsold1)*<span class="number">60</span>;</span><br><span class="line">minsold1=<span class="built_in">Math</span>.floor((e_hrsold1-hrsold1)*<span class="number">60</span>);</span><br><span class="line">seconds1=<span class="built_in">Math</span>.floor((e_minsold1-minsold1)*<span class="number">60</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">document</span>.getElementById(<span class="string">"djclock"</span>).innerHTML =<span class="string">'博客已运行&lt;span style="color:#E68321"&gt;'</span>+daysold1+<span class="string">"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;天&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=\"color:#E68321\"&gt;"</span>+hrsold1+<span class="string">"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;小时&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=\"color:#E68321\"&gt;"</span>+minsold1+<span class="string">"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;分&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=\"color:#E68321\"&gt;"</span>+seconds1+<span class="string">"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;秒&lt;/strong&gt;"</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">setInterval(<span class="string">"THINPIGServerTime1()"</span>,<span class="number">250</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&lt;<span class="regexp">/script&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><hr><h1 id="加入主题设置数据备份与恢